{
  "stem": "1033.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You seemed to somehow-- you're sucked up by your own being.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you're cognizant of people around you, and they're all shadows, dragging themselves, breathing like yourself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there is very little interaction, what you would call, except lining up for appels, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one thing that, of course, I cannot forget-- the first selection inside the gypsy camp came on Rosh Hashanah of 1944.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was-- I don't think it was by accident.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was selected to-- because by then, I was very skinny.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Mengele pointed one way, and I saw that all the skinny people went in one group and the fat ones, or the better, not as skinny, on the other.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And behind him, I scooted into the other group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I manage to get away with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Somebody else did it minutes after me, and he was caught and thrown back in the other group.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And these people were locked up in a block for a day or two, and then that was a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Bells ringing, and that meant nobody was allowed to come out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when it ended, that block was emptied.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Trucks came-- you could hear trucks coming-- and they were gone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when this same thing happened two weeks later, many of the people had a skin condition.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And somehow or other, Mengele was convinced to give them another chance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was in that group, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in that group, I got caught.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they locked us up in one of these blocks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was a boy with me whose brother was still on the other side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "His name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Vol ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he was from [INAUDIBLE], the same village as my grandmother's family came from, my grandmother's parents.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
